"No more Credits? Ah crap... But i had lot of fun! Thanks all. =)"

Smiley post-hume. Some says i live my life as it was a roleplaying game. Maybe it's true, life is a kind of big game!

My LJ kept complaining about its emptniess. I'll give him a meme :P nd just because i can't wait for the EF! o/ (Stolen from
greyshay
)


Where will you be most of the time during the day/s?

Exploring the convention i guess. I think 'ill be running around with my cell phone and the battery charger to find people i'd like to see :3

Where are you staying?

Erh...that's a good question and i haven't think about that one. I have my room but i don't know the hotel. The main hotel ,that's all i know :P

When are you arriving/leaving?

One day earlier and one day later. I come with friends so I obey to their choice of departure :D And i won't complain to spend more time to the EF bwehehe

Who will you be with?

Doh! I hope a lot of people i know and appreciate :P

Do you do free art?

If being silly and crazy is an art, then sure, it would be a pleasure to share it =D

Do you do trades?

Not really =)

Do you do commissions?

Commissions? First i need something to create, and i'm not that creative :P

What is your gender?

Male male male and male again :3

How old are you?

Why don't you just try to guess? ;3 There's a hint: it's above 18 =P

Can I touch you?

Touch me? Well some tried :P You can try too, but the effects will change from the place you touch. It can go from explosions, to laughs and also hugs or "balls" kicking =P

Can I talk to you?

Please do!! Do eeeeeet! I just hope my french accent won't kill you. But i really love chatting with people so you're more than welcome! =)

What are you going to be drinking?

LEMONADE! I know, maybe you think it's lame, but sugar has the same effect on me than alcohol and i'm scared to know how i could be if i were dwunk =D

Warf guys !

Mhmm? What's happening to me? I wanna write some journal? Alright xD

I feel really great these days for some reason and i wanted to write my happiness down somewhere ^.^

Anyways, the wolf is really happy for some days! n__n Good things is happening to him! Yay! My problems with school seem to stop little by little. I'd like to thank all my dear friends who helped me to not give up! Thanks guys! ^__^

What else...Oh yeah, one of my life's objective is about to happen! I'm going to live in a different country! This is something i always wanted to do! I really love travelling, but living in a different country is something special i want to try. So i have some months to get my license and a car <^^"

Oh and just for the end, it seems that my sentimental life is kinda...GREAT these days xD That should explain why i'm so overjoyed!

Anyways! Have a good day and take care guys! (And girls)

Warf! Tammy.
